            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong>, <strong>remaining chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>dried oregano </strong>and <strong>tomato paste</strong> in a bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> – these are your <strong>tomatoey breadcrumbs</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1686133789657-x200.jpg",
