            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the cheese sauce has thickened, add the <strong>macaroni</strong> and mix it all together – this is your <strong>mac 'n' cheese mixture</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>mac 'n' cheese mixture</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> and top with the <strong>remaining torn mozzarella</strong>, <strong>sliced pepperoni</strong> and <strong>tomatoey breadcrumbs</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 10-12 min or until golden and bubbling – this is your <strong>pepperoni pizza mac 'n' cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
