      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mac 'n' cheese is in the oven, wash your <strong>salad</strong> then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Combine your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>in a bowl – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>salad</strong> and <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong> to the <strong>dressing</strong> and toss – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
